  "texts": [
    "• Faster R-CNN (Region-based Convolutional Neural Network): Displays an accuracy of 69%, representing a tradeoff between accuracy and speed compared to YOLOv5 and SSD.",
    "• Mask R-CNN: Exhibits a lower accuracy of 61.06%, likely influenced by the additional complexity introduced by its instance segmentation capabilities.",
    "Average Prediction Time• YOLOv5: Boasts the lowest average time at 0.357 seconds, reinforcing its suitability for real-time applications.",
    "• SSD: Presents an average time of 0.72 seconds, indicating a reasonable balance between speed and accuracy.",
    "• Faster R-CNN: Exhibits an average time of 6.57 seconds, showcasing a comparable performance to SSD."
  ]
